                Wrist Control is a web platform for controlling your browser's pages using a #[span.docsTextHighlight Pebble]. There's a <a href="/marketplace" target="_blank">#[span.chromeStoreLink Marketplace]</a> where you can browse and download tailored plugins which are built to control a multitude of sites. With Wrist Control you can also customize your <span class="docsTextHighlight">Pebble's</span> controls through the Google Chrome extension. 
