                - First, install the #[span.docsTextHighlight Wrist ctrl] app from the #[span.docsTextHighlight Pebble] app on your phone.
                <br>
                - Install the chrome extension <a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/category/extensions" target="_blank">#[span.chromeStoreLink here]</a>.
                <br>
                - Click on the newly installed chrome extension:   <img class="iconImage"/> 
                <br>
                - Copy your <span class="channelText">Channel ID: <span class="firstColor"> XXXX</span></span> into your #[span.docsTextHighlight Pebble] app.
                <br>
                - Visit the <a href="/marketplace" target="_blank">#[span.chromeStoreLink Wrist Control Marketplace]</a> and install some nifty plugins!
                <br>
            h2.getStarted Creating Your Own Plugin
